{"tid":179490,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"擺低你最鍾意王菲嘅唱嘅歌詞","createTime":"2017-03-30T09:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T13:02:53.000Z","uid":1878,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae92bd080a3964ce308d5160ddb037ba88828784","tid":179490,"uid":1878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"華人嚟講王菲係最勁嗰批<br />\n好多歌都好正，不過最鍾意都係林夕寫俾佢嘅廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n約定<br />\n剪影的你輪廓 太好看 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F06ZcAEJ3IA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF06ZcAEJ3IA&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=df8d495b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F06ZcAEJ3IA</a><br />\n<br />\n曖昧<br />\n陪你輕乎着煙圈 到唇邊講不出滿足<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tC-k3-w9A8M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtC-k3-w9A8M&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=298d8869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tC-k3-w9A8M</a><br />\n<br />\n匆匆那年 都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/omobhuutrE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FomobhuutrE4&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4b3ce2de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/omobhuutrE4</a>"},{"pid":"6b82f0a73236ef4f8e17a14a2342584f6bd38955","tid":179490,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"Na Na Na ~~<br />\nNa Na Na~~"},{"pid":"8e9c0708da8f3327ee82fad9b2da3242600f1ed9","tid":179490,"uid":1878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"寫這高貴情書 在夜闌轉轉"},{"pid":"ebb597458342c305adf2f34265aec49df9cc2b7a","tid":179490,"uid":1878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"仍未熱戀已失戀"},{"pid":"728eaba1bade120d17892d748f12cdb85